data.description: Open Houses - Come check out this fabulous home on Saturday, February 3rd from 12:00 to 3:00 pm and Sunday, February 4th from 12:00 to 3:00 pm! Step into this inviting home where the heart of family life unfolds in a spacious and open floor plan. The focal point of the house is a generously sized living room that seamlessly connects to both the kitchen, breakfast area and dining room, creating a harmonious and inclusive living space.  The kitchen has granite throughout and an island. The living room, dining room and master bedroom have beautiful hardwood floors.  A second bedroom and bath downstairs offer convenience and flexibility.  Venturing upstairs, there is a dedicated game room. Whether you're entertaining guests or enjoying quality family time, this versatile space is perfect for a variety of activities. Two additional bedrooms and a bath on the upper level provide ample accommodation for family members or guests.  The home is equipped with a sleek array of solar panels seamlessly integrated into its roof and allows the homeowners to benefit from reduced energy bills.  Step outside onto the custom 35 x 10 deck, where you can savor the fresh air and unwind dining or relaxation. This well-designed two-story house offers a perfect balance of functionality and aesthetic appeal, providing a warm and welcoming atmosphere for its residents.
